The answer to your question is that the RFCs do not specify a
standard mechanism for relative naming.  However, this topic came
up once or twice on namedroppers in the past, probably about a year
ago.  There was quite a lot of discussion about it.  I suggest you
sift through the archives of the list, extract the important points,
and summarize them to namedroppers if you want to start this 
discussion again.  I think it's a worthwhile topic myself (having
flamed about it before).

Peter
